<info gid="3099393622" type="Plot Summary">The Godom Empire, a Nazi power, ruled by Tathagata Killer attempts to conquer the world with advanced technology the world has never seen. Meanwhile Sho Shishimaru, a doctor working for an international charity, is also a member of a behind the scenes organization called “Hermes’ Wings” that resists the Empire. He is gifted with occasional psychic visions of the future which eventually alert him that Japan will be taken over by Godom. After being saved by Buddhist monks during an attack he is informed that they believe he is the reincarnation of Buddha and the Savior; the light of hope. He is tasked with saving earth and humanity from sure doom along with helping hands from fellow humans, spirits, and even aliens.</info>
